M|Code|tx|\| Skill references \| Codex equivalent \|
M|Code|tx|\|-----------------\|------------------\|
M|Code|tx|\| `Task` tool (dispatch subagent) \| `spawn_agent` (see [Named ag dispatch](#named-ag-dispatch)) \|
